  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK584">
<l>viṉaiceyvār tañcuṟṟam vēṇṭātā reṉṟāṅ </l>
<l>kaṉaivaraiyu mārāyva toṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is a spy who watches all men, to wit, those who are in the king's employment, his relatives, and his enemies.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
